### 3. GotchiMood Class

**Purpose**: Manage 100 mood states and temporary mood overlays.

**Mood Categories**:

#### Primary Survival/Emotional Moods (0-9)
| Mood | Index | Description | Trigger |
|------|-------|-------------|---------|
| MOOD_00_HAPPY | 0 | Content and playful | Balanced stats |
| MOOD_01_EXCITED | 1 | Energetic and active | High energy, high excitement |
| MOOD_02_SATISFIED | 2 | Peaceful and relaxed | Low needs, content |
| MOOD_03_BORED | 3 | Unstimulated | Low excitement, low satisfaction |
| MOOD_04_HUNGRY | 4 | Needs food | High food level (hunger) |
| MOOD_05_THIRSTY | 5 | Needs drink | High hydration need |
| MOOD_06_SLEEPY | 6 | Needs rest | High sleep debt, low energy |
| MOOD_07_SICK | 7 | Ill | Low health, high disease |
| MOOD_08_SAD | 8 | Upset | Low happiness |
| MOOD_09_ANGRY | 9 | Frustrated | High hunger/sick, low satisfaction |

#### Extended Moods (10-99)
**Positive/Emotional (10-29)**: JOYFUL(10), CONTENT(11), RELIEVED(12), CALM(13), PEACEFUL(14), SERENE(15), OPTIMISTIC(16), HOPEFUL(17), CURIOUS(18), INTERESTED(19), FOCUSED(20), DETERMINED(21), PROUD(22), SUCCESSFUL(23), GRATEFUL(24), LOVED(25), SAFE(26), SECURE(27), TRUSTING(28), AFFECTIONATE(29), LOVING(30)

**Activity-Based (30-39)**: PLAYFUL(31), EXPLORING(32), ADVENTUROUS(33), CREATING(34), LEARNING(35), ACHIEVING(36), COMPETITIVE(37), COLLABORATIVE(38), TEACHING(39), HELPING(40)

**Positive/State (40-59)**: GIVING(41), GENEROUS(42), ABUNDANT(43), PROSPEROUS(44), HEALTHY(45), FIT(46), ENERGETIC(47), VIBRANT(48), ALIVE(49), SPIRITED(50), CHARMING(51), BEAUTIFUL(52), GLORIOUS(53), MAGNIFICENT(54), WONDERFUL(55), AMAZING(56), INCREDIBLE(57), EXTRAORDINARY(58), SUPERB(59), FANTASTIC(60), AWESOME(61), MIRACULOUS(62), DIVINE(63), ETHEREAL(64), SPIRITUAL(65)

**Intellectual (65-74)**: MINDFUL(66), WISE(67), KNOWLEDGEABLE(68), INTELLIGENT(69), CLEVER(70), SKILLFUL(71), EXPERT(72), MASTER(73), GRANDMASTER(74)

**Legendary (75-99)**: LEGENDARY(75), MYTHICAL(76), EPIC(77), HEROIC(78), VALIANT(79), NOBLE(80), VIRTUOUS(81), RIGHTEOUS(82), FAIR(83), JUST(84), BALANCED(85), HARMONIOUS(86), SYNCED(87), ALIGNED(88), CONNECTED(89), UNITED(90), ONE(91), WHOLE(92), COMPLETE(93), FULL(94), BLOOMING(95), THRIVING(96), GROWING(97), EVOLVING(98), TRANSFORMING(99)

**Mood Properties**:
| Property | Type | Description |
|----------|------|-------------|
| name | string | Display name |
| description | string | Human-readable description |
| tint | Color | Color overlay for rendering |
| priority | float | How strongly this mood drives behavior |
| requiresAction | bool | Whether player intervention is needed |
| actionNeeded | string | What action the gotchi needs |
| energyImpact | float | Effect on energy drain rate |
| socialImpact | float | Effect on desire for interaction |

