## Interaction Methods

### Gotchi Interaction Functions

| Function | Parameters | Effects |
|----------|------------|---------|
| `interact()` | None | +15 Happiness, +20 Excitement, +1 Friendship, sets "play" action (2s) |
| `feed()` | None | -30 Hunger, +10 Energy, sets "eat" action (3s) |
| `play()` | None | +25 Excitement, +20 Happiness, +1 Agility, sets "play" action (4s) |
| `clean()` | None | Sets Cleanliness to 100, sets "idle" action (1s) |
| `heal()` | None | Sets Health to 100, +5 Happiness |
| `sleep()` | None | Sets sleeping_ = true, "sleep" action |
| `wake()` | None | Sets sleeping_ = false, clears overlays |
| `setTargetPosition(v)` | Vector2 | Sets target for movement, sets "move" action |
| `moveToTarget(dt)` | float | Moves toward target position |
| `wander(dt)` | float | Sets random wander direction |

---

## Tick Life Cycle

### The Gotchi Tick Lifecycle (1.0 second intervals)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    Gotchi::update(float deltaTime)                      │
│                    Called at 60 FPS (or game speed)                     │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                         │
│  1. Dead Check                                                          │
│     └─ if (dead_) return;  // Exit early if dead                       │
│                                                                         │
│  2. Timing Updates                                                      │
│     ├─ tickTimer_ += deltaTime                                          │
│     └─ lastUpdate_ += deltaTime                                         │
│                                                                         │
│  3. SceneActor Base Update                                              │
│     └─ SceneActor::update(deltaTime)  // Physics, collision, etc.      │
│                                                                         │
│  4. TICK BOUNDARY CHECK (tickTimer_ >= 1.0s)                           │
│     ├─ Calculate ticks elapsed                                          │
│     └─ Reset tickTimer_ for remainder                                   │
│                                                                         │
│     ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│     │                    updateStats(float ticks)                   │   │
│     │  Core Vital Stats Drain (per tick):                           │   │
│     │    • Food Level:    +5.0  (hunger increases)                  │   │
│     │    • Hydration:     +3.0  (thirst increases)                  │   │
│     │    • Sleep Debt:    +2.0  (sleep need increases)              │   │
│     │    • Energy:        -3.0  (drains naturally)                  │   │
│     │    • Cleanliness:   -2.0  (gets dirty slowly)                 │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Emotional Stats Decay:                                       │   │
│     │    • Happiness:     -1.0  (natural decay)                     │   │
│     │    • Excitement:    -0.5  (calms down)                        │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Natural Recovery (non-sleeping):                             │   │
│     │    • Energy:        +0.5  (slow recovery)                     │   │
│     │    • Vitality:      +0.2  (slow healing)                      │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Natural Recovery (SLEEPING):                                 │   │
│     │    • Energy:        +5.0  (5x faster recovery)                │   │
│     │    • Sleep Debt:    -8.0  (8x faster recovery)                │   │
│     │    • Happiness:     +1.0  (sleep makes happy)                 │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Health Impact Calculations:                                  │   │
│     │    • Hunger > 80:     -2.0 health/tick                        │   │
│     │    • Thirst > 80:     -2.0 health/tick                        │   │
│     │    • Sleep Debt > 80: -1.5 health/tick                        │   │
│     │    • Dirty > 70:      -1.0 health/tick                        │   │
│     │    • Happiness < 20:  -1.0 health/tick                        │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Health Cap:                                                   │   │
│     │    • Max health clamped to 100                                │   │
│     │    • Death trigger at health <= 0                             │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Stat Clamping:                                                │   │
│     │    • All stats normalized to 0-100 range                      │   │
│     └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                         │
│  5. MOOD UPDATE                                                       │
│     └─ mood_.updateMood(deltaTime, stats_)                             │
│                                                                         │
│     ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│     │              GotchiMood::updateMood()                         │   │
│     │  Score each primary mood based on stats:                      │   │
│     │    • Hunger Score:   food_level * 30                          │   │
│     │    • Thirst Score:   hydration * 25                           │   │
│     │    • Sleep Score:    sleep_debt * 30                          │   │
│     │    • Energy Score:   (energy > 0.7) ? (energy-0.7)*30 : 0     │   │
│     │    • Hygiene Score:  (1-hygiene) * 20                         │   │
│     │    • Happy Score:    happiness * 40                           │   │
│     │    • Sad Score:      (1-happiness) * 25                       │   │
│     │    • Excited Score:  excitement * 30                          │   │
│     │    • Bored Score:    (1-satisfaction) * 30                    │   │
│     │    • Lonely Score:   (1-friends) * 15                         │   │
│     │    • Sick Score:     (1-health) * 35                          │   │
│     │                                                               │   │
│     │  Find dominant mood (highest score > 10)                      │   │
│     │  Default: SATISFIED if no strong needs                        │   │
│     └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                         │
│  6. MOOD OVERLAYS PROCESSING                                          │
│     └─ mood_.processMoodOverlays(deltaTime)                            │
│                                                                         │
│     ┌───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │
│     │              GotchiMood::processMoodOverlays()                │   │
│     │  1. Decay all overlay durations by deltaTime                  │   │
│     │  2. Remove expired overlays                                   │   │
│     │  3. Update overlayTimer to most recent overlay                │   │
│     └───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │
│                                                                         │
│  7. ACTION TIMER UPDATE                                               │
│     ├─ actionTimer_ -= deltaTime                                        │
│     └─ if (actionTimer_ <= 0) {                                         │
│           if (!sleeping_ && currentAction_ != "idle") {                 │
│               setAction("idle");  // Return to idle                      │
│           }                                                              │
│         }                                                                │
│                                                                         │
│  8. DEBUG OUTPUT (if enabled)                                         │
│     └─ Every 5 ticks, print:                                           │
│        "[Gotchi] Tick N | Mood: X | Hunger: Y | Energy: Z"             │
│                                                                         │
│  9. ANIMATION UPDATE                                                  │
│     └─ updateAnimation(deltaTime)  // Called from SceneActor            │
│                                                                         │
│  10. WANDER LOGIC (if not sleeping, idle action)                      │
│      ├─ wanderTimer_ -= deltaTime                                       │
│      └─ if (wanderTimer_ <= 0) {                                        │
│            wander(deltaTime);  // Pick random direction                 │
│            wanderTimer_ = 2.0 to 3.5 seconds                           │
│         }                                                                │
│                                                                         │
│  11. TARGET MOVEMENT (if target set)                                  │
│      └─ if (targetPosition_ != {0,0}) {                                │
│            moveToTarget(deltaTime);                                     │
│         }                                                                │
│                                                                         │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## Animation States

### Action Types

| Action | Duration | Animation Speed | Loop | Description |
|--------|----------|-----------------|------|-------------|
| idle | infinite | 0.2s/frame | yes | Default standing state |
| move | continuous | 0.1s/frame | yes | Walking/running animation |
| eat | 3.0s | 0.15s/frame | no | Eating animation (non-looping) |
| sleep | infinite | 0.3s/frame | yes | Sleeping animation |
| play | actionTimer | 0.1s/frame | no | Playful animation (duration varies) |
| sad | continuous | 0.25s/frame | yes | Sad/depressed animation |
| happy | continuous | 0.15s/frame | yes | Happy/joyful animation |

### Animation Frame Files (Expected Format)
```
animations/gotchi/
├── idle_00.png
├── idle_01.png
├── move_00.png
├── move_01.png
├── eat_00.png
├── eat_01.png
├── sleep_00.png
├── sleep_01.png
├── play_00.png
├── play_01.png
├── sad_00.png
├── sad_01.png
├── happy_00.png
├── happy_01.png
```

