## Statistical Relationships

### Mood-Stat Correlations

| Mood | Primary Triggers | Secondary Influences |
|------|-----------------|---------------------|
| HUNGRY | FOOD_LEVEL > 70 | LOW ENERGY, LOW HAPPINESS |
| SLEEPY | SLEEP_DEBT > 60 | LOW ENERGY, LOW HAPPINESS |
| SICK | FITNESS < 50 | LOW ENERGY, LOW HAPPINESS |
| BORED | SATISFACTION < 30 | LOW EXCITEMENT, LOW FRIENDSHIP |
| SAD | HAPPINESS < 30 | LOW LOVE, LOW PEACE |
| EXCITED | EXCITEMENT > 70 | HIGH ENERGY, HIGH HAPPINESS |
| HAPPY | HAPPINESS > 70 | LOW HUNGER, LOW SLEEP_DEBT |
| CALM | SATISFACTION > 60 | LOW ANXIETY, LOW ANGER |

### Action Effects Matrix

| Action | Hunger | Energy | Happiness | Excitement | Health |
|--------|--------|--------|-----------|------------|--------|
| feed | -30 | +10 | +10 | 0 | 0 |
| play | 0 | -10 | +20 | +25 | +1 |
| interact | 0 | 0 | +15 | +20 | 0 |
| clean | 0 | 0 | +10 | 0 | +5 |
| heal | 0 | 0 | +5 | 0 | +100 |
| sleep | 0 | +5/tick | +1/tick | 0 | +0.2/tick |

